h2 Add new item
div(class='form-group')
	label(for='title') Title:
	input(ng-model='form.title', name='title', class='form-control', placeholder='Enter the item you want to buy')	
div(class='form-group')
	label(for='text') Description (Text):
	textarea(ng-model='form.text', name='text', cols='50', rows='15',class='form-control')
button(ng-click='addItem()', class='btn btn-primary') Add Item